Settings for Linux, using the gfortran compiler that comes with the GCC of
version 4.0.0 and up. (See g95 for the Fortran 90 compiler distributed 
separately from GCC.)

Requires the following environment settings:

ESMF_COMPILER gfortran

Defaults to a 64-bit build, set this for 32-bit systems:

ESMF_PREC 32

